name: o11
long_description:
o11 brings extreme operational efficiency to firms of any size. Seamlessly integrated into every Microsoft 365 tool, o11 transforms your documents, decks, spreadsheets, and files into a dynamic knowledge layer that drives research, modeling, and client ready deliverables with consistent precision. We're the first company to build a full-featured AI native execution layer within the entire Microsoft 365 suite.

o11's services are available to financial firms, enterprise organizations, and Office 365 power users.
one_liner: The Most Integrated M365 AI Suite
